    "description": "Take your chess game beyond the limits of a physical board! Non-Euclidean Chess is a chess engine which supports custom board types - many of which defy traditional movement rules, or even physical limitations.<br><br>Non-Euclidean Chess is also the only chess game where you can play with <i>any</i> number of players. Do you and 100 of your best friends want to play? We can't promise it will be quick, but you can do it!<br><br><strong>Choose from the following gamemodes:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> N-Player Chess<br></li><li> Hyperbolic (Poincare Disk) Chess<br></li><li> Cubic Chess<br></li><li> Toroidal Chess<br></li><li> Battle Royale Chess<br></li><li> Chesseract<br></li><li> Growth Chess<br></li><li> Slider Chess</li></ul><br>Plus many more modes and minor variations!",
